726128f-a.title: Queens: Bayside Avenue - Parsons Boulevard
726128f-a.text:
Bayside Avenue, at the S.E. corner of Parsons Boulevard, showing a private home of nineteenth century construction.
The view is from the Boulevard.
P. L. Sperr  April 13, 1927
